comments: Bridges (PHX) makes contact with Reddick (NOP) that affects his SQBR.
Booker (PHX) makes marginal contact to Holiday (NOP) during his drive.
Booker (PHX) extends his arm to Holiday's (NOP) body and dislodges him from his legal guarding position.
Bridges (PHX) makes marginal arm contact with Holiday (NOP) at the end of his drive prior to the release of the pass.
Booker (PHX) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Ingram (NOP) and does not deliver contact.
Holiday (NOP) makes marginal contact as Booker (PHX) lunges forward, but Booker loses control of the ball due to contact from Saric's (PHX) leg.
Hayes (NOP) makes marginal contact with Booker (PHX) as he tries to secure the loose ball.
Holiday (NOP) and Rubio (PHX) make contact with each other as both players attempt to secure the loose ball.
Saric (PHX) establishes himself in a legal position when he sets the pick on Ball (NOP) as he does not deliver contact.
Bridges (PHX) makes marginal body contact with Ingram (NOP) during the rebound.
Saric (PHX) cleanly dislodges the ball from Ingram's (NOP) possession.
Saric (PHX) makes lower body contact with Ingram (NOP) that dislodges him during the rebound.
Kaminsky (PHX) does not establish himself in Holiday's (NOP) path and extends his knee into Holiday's leg during the screen.
Williams (NOP) and Saric (PHX) engage and disengage during the rebound.
Bridges (PHX) makes marginal contact with Ingram (NOP) as Ingram secures the pass.
Bridges (PHX) has a resting hand to Ingram's (NOP) off-arm and releases prior to Ingram's upward shooting motion.
Kaminsky (PHX) establishes himself in Ingram's (NOP) path during the pick and does not deliver contact.
Oubre Jr. (PHX) maintains his legal guarding position as he defends Holiday (NOP) and does not affect his SQBR.
Oubre Jr. (PHX) maintains his legal guarding position as Holiday (NOP) initiates the contact and makes clean contact with the ball during Holiday's shot attempt.
Rubio (PHX) and Reddick (NOP) engage and disengage off-ball.
Johnson (PHX) makes marginal contact with Ingram (NOP) as both players attempt to secure the loose ball.

Kaminsky (PHX) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Holiday (NOP) and does not deliver contact.
LAR shows Holiday (NOP) grabs Booker (PHX) during the screen and affects his FOM.
Kaminsky (PHX) establishes himself Holiday's (NOP) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.

Hayes (NOP) maintains his legal guarding position as he defends Hayes' (NOP) drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Ball (NOP) establishes himself in Johnson's (PHX) path during the pick and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Booker (PHX) establishes himself in Hayes' (NOP) path during the pick and does not deliver contact.
Kaminsky (PHX) holds Ingram's (NOP) arm and affects his ability to defend the incoming pass.

Holiday (NOP) makes incidental contact to Oubre Jr. (PHX) during his drive to the basket.
Oubre Jr. (PHX) gives Holiday (NOP) room to land on the jump shot attempt.
Hayes (NOP) and Booker (PHX) make marginal contact with each other as both players attempt to secure the loose ball rebound.
Holiday (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Johnson (PHX) and does not deliver contact.
